《'''密探'''》（{{Kor|k=밀정|hj=密偵}}，{{lang-en|''The Age of Shadows''}}，前稱作{{lang|en|''Secret Agent''}}）是一部2016年韓國[[剧情片|剧情片]]，由[[金知雲|金知雲]]執導和撰寫劇本，[[宋康昊|宋康昊]]和[[孔劉|孔劉]]主演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2016/08/141_211425.html|title=Movie sheds light on Japanese occupation|date=2016-08-08|publisher=|accessdate=2016-09-23|archive-date=2016-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160923082326/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2016/08/141_211425.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/news/news.jsp?mode=VIEW&seq=3966|title=AGE OF SHADOWS, CITY OF MADNESS, HANDMAIDEN Selected for Toronto|publisher=|accessdate=2016-09-23|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113075923/http://www.koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/news/news.jsp?mode=VIEW&seq=3966|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年9月3日在[[第73屆威尼斯影展|第73屆威尼斯影展]]上全球首映，2016年9月7日在韓國上映。上映後大獲好評，並在韓國創下750萬觀影人次的優異票房；《密探》被選定於[[第89屆奧斯卡金像獎|第89屆奧斯卡金像獎]]上代表韓國角逐[[奧斯卡最佳外語片獎|最佳外語片]]<ref name="SouthKorea">{{cite web |url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2016/08/30/0200000000AEN20160830009100315.html |title=S. Korean film "The Age of Shadows" submitted to Oscars |work=Yonhap News |date=2016-08-30 |accessdate=2016-08-30 |archive-date=2016-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902023603/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2016/08/30/0200000000AEN20160830009100315.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Variety">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/asia/age-of-shadows-picked-as-koreas-oscar-contender-1201847524/ |title=Warner Bros.’ ‘Age of Shadows’ Picked as Korea’s Oscar Contender |last=Kil |first=Sonia |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2016-08-30 |accessdate=2016-08-30 |archive-date=2016-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008205415/http://variety.com/2016/film/asia/age-of-shadows-picked-as-koreas-oscar-contender-1201847524/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20160831000308|title=‘The Age of Shadows’ selected as 2017 Oscars contender|first=The Korea|last=Herald|date=2016-08-31|publisher=|accessdate=2016-09-23|archive-date=2016-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922171706/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20160831000308|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2016/09/02/79/0200000000AEN20160902008300315F.html|title=(Moview Review) The Age of Shadows, commanding double-spy film|publisher=|accessdate=2016-09-23|archive-date=2016-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924061220/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2016/09/02/79/0200000000AEN20160902008300315F.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20160826000772|title=Director Kim Jee-woon says ‘Age of Shadows’ is ‘heated’ noir|first=The Korea|last=Herald|da